   each particle, including realistic treatment of                5825 1451
   discrete transitions                                           5825 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL-2 library [Ri03]              5825 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                5825 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               5825 1451
   and gamma strength functions  based on the RIPL-2              5825 1451
   library [Ri03]                                                 5825 1451
